      • search

        public JSONObject search(Configuration cloudConfig,
                         SalesforceSearchParameters parameters,
                         ResourceResolver resolver)
                  throws SalesforceException
        Uses the SalesforceClient to search leads
        Parameters:
        cloudConfig - Salesforce Cloud Service Configuration used for identifying Salesforce Account.
        parameters - Search Parameters used via searching
        resolver - The current ResourceResolver object used if the access token expires during the search and we need to save the new access token in the configuration.
        Returns:
        JSON object consisting of leads information
        Throws:
        SalesforceException
